# Maintenance Service

## Developer and Novice Friendly
Specifically created with both developers and novice users in mind. Allowing for
seemless integration in to an extended project or a basic installation

## View Maintenance Tasks
This application fully integrates in to the Dashboard to show enabled / disabled maintenance applications at a glance
- Automatic detection and installation of new maintenance services
- Each application has control of it's own settings and locations
- Runs each application on a per domain basis making it possible to use quotas
